          "name": "Ensure select dse-k8s-hosted microservices can run active/active",
          "description": {
            "raw": "While we [[ https://phabricator.wikimedia.org/T408643 | added a second dse-k8s cluster in CODFW ]],  we never completed the necessary steps for our hosted services to run active/active. \n\nThere's not much use to having a second cluster if we can't do active/active for services, so I'm creating this ticket to:\n[x] Complete all steps necessary for select dse-k8s services to run active/active*\n[x] Verify operation\n\n*Not all services can or should run active/active. For the purposes of this ticket, we're scoping to `opensearch-ipoid` and `opensearch-test`.\n"
